{"search_data": "Himachal PradeshSenior Citizen Health Insurance Scheme (SCHIS) in Himachal PradeshHighlights of Senior Citizen Health Insurance Scheme (SCHIS)Below are some of the main features / highlights of the SCHISThe benefit of SCHIS is available to senior citizen (above 60 years).The candidate should be Rashtriya Swasthya Bima Yojna (RSBY) smart card holder.The beneficiary has to pay only a nominal annual premium for SCHIS which is up to Rs. 500 per family.Moreover, Central and State government will share the insurance premium in the ratio of 90:10 under the Trust Model.In addition, the state government will not issue any separate enrollment process. The beneficiary will be selected only among the smart card holders of RSBY.The beneficiary can take health care services by showing their health card into any of the RSBY empaneled hospitals.All the financial transactions between government and insurance company will be done through bank channel. Apart from this, the unspent fund will be refunded at the closing of the financial year.The candidates can check the name of nearly hospital by clicking on the below link RSBY Empaneled hospitalsSurgical Packages List Ministry of health and Family Welfare has prepared a separate list of the surgical packages that costs more than Rs 30,000. Below given is the list of those packagesSurgical OncologyCardiothoracic SurgeryPoly-Trauma and RepairNeuro SurgeryMedical OncologyCardiologyBurnsCardiovascular SurgeryThe beneficiary can avail cashless treatment in any of the RSBY empaneled hospitals under Senior Citizen Health Insurance Scheme (SCHIS). Moreover, the government is also providing two additional covers that will be compensated from existing top-up of RSBY for critical care up to Rs. 1.75 lakh in addition up to Rs. 2.25 lakh for cancer.The trust/ society will receive the claims directly from the hospitals. Subsequently, these trusts will settle these claims on the basis of the package rates defined by the Central govt. Furthermore, state govt. will borne the expenses for IEC and other certain expenses.The Trust Model will get all claims directly from the hospitals, not to the beneficiary and will settle claims in accordance with the defined package rates.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}